# Rust build artifacts (also redirected outside OneDrive via .cargo/config.toml)
/target
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb

# Cargo.lock IS committed for a binary/app — do not ignore it.

# WebView2 / browser runtime data (profiles, caches) if created inside the repo
/userdata/
/profiles/
*.ldb
*.log

# Secrets — never commit Bitwarden session keys or tokens
.env
*.session
bw-session.txt

# Personal / internal docs + machine-specific build config — keep local, out of the public repo
.cargo/config.toml
/SESSION_LOG.md
/PLAN.md
/CLAUDE.md

# OS / editor
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
.vscode/
